Eldians.name: Eren Yeager
Eldians.quotes: I'm Gonna Destroy Them! Every Last One Of Those Animals That's On This Earth!

Eldians.name: Erwin Smith
Eldians.quotes: This Moment! This Battle! Humanity's Continued Survival Depends On It! So Once More, For Humanity's Sake... Dedicate Your Hearts!

Eldians.name: Levi Ackerman
Eldians.quotes: The only thing we’re allowed to do is believe that we won’t regret the choice we made.

Eldians.name: Hange Zoë
Eldians.quotes: I Led Us All To This Point. I Kept Moving Forward, Even If It Meant Killing So Many Of My Comrades. It's Time I Take Responsibility For That.

Eldians.name: Dot Pixis
Eldians.quotes: I Led Us All To This Point. I Kept Moving Forward, Even If It Meant Killing So Many Of My Comrades. It's Time I Take Responsibility For That.

Eldians.name: Mikasa Ackerman
Eldians.quotes: If You Think It's Natural For People To Die For Others. I'm Sure You'll Understand That At Times, The Sacrifice Of A Single Precious Life Can Save Many Others.

Eldians.name: Connie Springer
Eldians.quotes: I...want to become a soldier my mother would be proud of. So...let's go and save some people in trouble.

Eldians.name: Floch Forster
Eldians.quotes: If Eren dies, Paradis will sink under a sea of blood!! The entire world will take vengeance on us! Your parents, your siblings, your children, they'll all be slaughtered!! Devote your hearts!!

Eldians.name: Sasha Braus
Eldians.quotes: It'll Be Fine, I'm Willing To Share. Oh, Can You Imagine The Sandwiches?

Eldians.name: Armin Arlert
Eldians.quotes: A person who cannot sacrifice everything, cannot change anything.
